        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哈，聪明话都让你说了，还要我干什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
